We thank all reviewers for their insightful comments and are highly encouraged that
Reviewer \textcolor[HTML]{25b262}{25b262}{zpit} noted that our work ``addressing two important challenges'' ``practical'' and ``excellent in presentation'';
Reviewer \textcolor[HTML]{d7872e}{YJGe} found our paper \emph{important for its focus on sparse rewards}, offered a \emph{valid perspective on rethinking sampling strategies beyond simply scaling models or reward engineering}, and considered it \emph{well-written and easy to follow};
